Locators :
1. ID
2. ClassName
3. Name
4. linkText -- <a> anchor tag
5. partialLinkText -- <a> anchor tag
6. Xpath
7. CSS

Xpath Syntax : //tagName[@attribute='value'];
if have to find in entire DOM, the syntax : //*[@attribute='value'];

Xpath parent child relationship : Define xpath for parent and traverse till child using /tagname

Relative xpath : direct node
Absolute : starting from html/parent node

sibling : //*[@attribute='value']/following-sibling::<sibling tagname>
parent : //*[child xpath]/parent::<parent tagname>

Text() : //*[text()=''];